T1  - THE POLITICS OF FDI EXPROPRIATION
AU  - Azzimonti, Marina
Y1  - 2018/05/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12277
T2  - International Economic Review
