T1  - BETTER LATER THAN NEVER? AN EXPERIMENT ON BARGAINING UNDER ADVERSE SELECTION
AU  - Bochet, Olivier
AU  - Siegenthaler, Simon
Y1  - 2018/05/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12292
